    {
      "text": "The graph depicting the post-mortem cooling process is typically expected to have what shape?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Hyperbolic"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Sigmoid"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Linear"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Parabolic"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 1,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Option B - Sigmoid:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>This is the characteristic shape of post-mortem cooling. The body cools gradually at first, reaches a midpoint, and then cools more rapidly.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/JFJWor5CROPgKPATxBMC1699592940.png\" /></p>\n\n<p><strong>Incorrect Options:</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Option A -</strong><strong> Hyperbolic:</strong> A hyperbolic curve would suggest rapid initial <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"579dcf5fc51692777185eef17a83c6\">cooling</span> followed by a slower decline, which is not characteristic of post-mortem cooling.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Option C -</strong><strong> Linear:</strong> This option implies a constant rate of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"579dcf5fc51692777185eef17a83c6\">cooling</span> over time. Again, the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"d02067c4b51692777191b8eec8b062\">linear</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"579dcf5fc51692777185eef17a83c6\">cooling</span> pattern doesn't accurately represent the post-mortem <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"579dcf5fc51692777185eef17a83c6\">cooling</span> process, which is more complex.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Option D -</strong><strong> Parabolic:</strong> A parabolic curve would imply a constant rate of cooling, which doesn't align with the observed pattern of post-mortem cooling.</p>",
